text.__SUMMARY__: Psychotria woytkowskii is a species of plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to Peru.
text.Sources: World Conservation Monitoring Centre (1998). "Psychotria woytkowskii". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T36983A10024290. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T36983A10024290.en. Retrieved 16 December 2017.
